com.avaya.csta.binding

Class LookAheadInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ecma.csta.CastorObject
      • com.avaya.csta.binding.LookAheadInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LookAheadInfo
extends ch.ecma.csta.CastorObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    Avaya LookAheadInfo
    LookAheadInfo Parameters
    type InterflowType Specifies the type of interflow associated with the call. The following values are supported:
    • noInterflow
    • allInterflow
    • thresholdInterflow
    • transferred
    • vectoringInterflow
    priority interflowPriority Specifies the priority the call was queued. The following values are supported:
    • notInQueue
    • low
    • medium
    • high
    • top
    hours int Specifies the hour of the time in which the call entered vector processing.
    minutes int Specifies the minutes of the time in which the call entered vector processing.
    seconds int Specifies the seconds of the time in which the call entered vector processing.
    sourceVDN DeviceID Specifies the name of the VDN that interflowed the call.
    Version:
    $Revision$ $Date$
